🧊 COLD STORAGE – Teaser Trailer (2026) | Liam Neeson 🔥
Some threats can’t be contained forever. Cold Storage is the chilling new action-thriller of 2026 starring Liam Neeson, where a deadly discovery buried deep in the past is about to resurface.

🔍 Film Overview:
When a government bioweapons facility suffers a catastrophic breach, a retired special operative (Liam Neeson) is pulled back into action to secure a classified underground “cold storage” vault. But what’s inside isn’t just dangerous — it’s alive… and it’s spreading. Racing against time, he must stop the outbreak before it reaches the surface and destroys everything.

💥 What to Expect:

High-stakes action fused with claustrophobic suspense...
Liam Neeson in a gritty, determined hero role...
Biohazard containment suits, tense close-quarters combat, and race-against-the-clock urgency...
A blend of Outbreak, The Thing, and Contagion...

⭐ Starring:
Liam Neeson
Joe Keery
Sosie Bacon
Lesley Manville
Vanessa Redgrave
